@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'DBS Servis Bilgileri'
@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
define view entity YDBS_DDL_I_SERVICE
  as select from ydbs_t_service
  association to parent YDBS_DDL_I_BANKS as _Banks on $projection.Bankinternalid = _Banks.Bankinternalid
{
  key bankinternalid    as Bankinternalid,
  key companycode       as Companycode,
      firm_code         as FirmCode,
      cpi_username      as CpiUsername,
      cpi_password      as CpiPassword,
      cpi_url           as CpiUrl,
      class_name        as ClassName,
      additional_field1 as AdditionalField1,
      additional_field2 as AdditionalField2,
      additional_field3 as AdditionalField3,
      additional_field4 as AdditionalField4,
      currency          as Currency,
      service_type      as ServiceType,
      username          as Username,
      password          as Password,
      class_suffix      as ClassSuffix,
      cpi_url2          as CpiUrl2,
      cpi_url3          as CpiUrl3,
      _Banks
}
